            <li>Practice previous years' question papers.</li>
            <li>Focus on time management during exams.</li>
          </ul>

          <ul>
            <li>Understand the GATE syllabus thoroughly.</li>
            <li>Practice previous years' question papers.</li>
            <li>Focus on time management during exams.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Quick Formula Recap</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Time Complexity: O(1), O(log n), O(n), etc.</li>
            <li>Sorting Algorithms: T(n) = O(n log n)</li>
            <li>Binary Search: Divide and conquer.</li>
          </ul>

          <ul>
            <li>Time Complexity: O(1), O(log n), O(n), etc.</li>
            <li>Sorting Algorithms: T(n) = O(n log n)</li>
            <li>Binary Search: Divide and conquer.</li>
          </ul>

          <ul>
            <li>Time Complexity: O(1), O(log n), O(n), etc.</li>
            <li>Sorting Algorithms: T(n) = O(n log n)</li>
            <li>Binary Search: Divide and conquer.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Highlight MCQ of the Day</h3>
          <div className="highlight-mcq">
            <p><strong>{highlightedMCQ.question}</strong></p>
            
          </div>
          <div className="highlight-mcq">
            <p><strong>{highlightedMCQ.question}</strong></p>
            
          </div>
          <div className="highlight-mcq">
            <p><strong>{highlightedMCQ.question}</strong></p>
            
          </div>
      </div>
      <button className="next-btn" onClick={handleNext}>
          Next
      </button>
      

    </>
  );
};

export default MCQ;
